room_title: Escape room "Save Tony" by Clueless Escape Rooms in Ann Arbor
review: We booked both Save Tony rooms and had a work competition. A lot of fun and interesting clues. One group saved Tony and the other didn't. Recommend!

room_title: Escape room "Save Tony" by Clueless Escape Rooms in Ann Arbor
review: There were 4 of us saving Tony - it was an absolute blast! This was the first escape room for 3 of us - but will definitely not be the last.
